OL,3,C'In 40 seconds, everything was gone':
OL,4,CThe village destroyed by climate change
OL,6,FDaniel Ritler had lived all his life
OL,7,Fin Blatten. The restaurant and
OL,8,Fdelicatessen he ran with his wife
OL,9,FKarin now lie under millions of tons
OL,10,Fof rock and mud, themselves invisible
OL,11,Funder millions of gallons of water.
OL,13,F"The whole thing happened within 40
OL,14,Fseconds. In 40 seconds, everything was
OL,15,Fgone. Houses that were built in 15 and
OL,16,F16 centuries were buried, all buried",
OL,17,Fhe told me.
