OL,3,C'In 40 seconds, everything was gone':
OL,4,CThe village destroyed by climate change
OL,6,FThe sheep Daniel kept in the pristine
OL,7,Falpine pastures above the village also
OL,8,Fsurvived, but whether they or the
OL,9,FRitlers will even be able to return is
OL,10,Funcertain, perhaps even unlikely.
OL,11,FFirst the geology of the Lotschental
OL,12,Fvalley must stabilise, and that itself
OL,13,Fcould take many years.
OL,15,FThis disaster was not caused solely by
OL,16,Fclimate change ` erosion and minor
OL,17,Fearthquakes in these mountains also
OL,18,Fplayed their part ` but there's little
OL,19,Fdoubt that without the significant
OL,20,Fwarming the Alps have seen in the last
OL,21,Ffew decades it wouldn't have happened.
