OL,3,C'In 40 seconds, everything was gone':
OL,4,CThe village destroyed by climate change
OL,6,FOn current trends, glaciologists
OL,7,Fconfidently predict that by the end of
OL,8,Fhis century, 2100, there will be no
OL,9,Fmore glaciers in Switzerland. This
OL,10,Fdoesn't just mean a lot of melt-water:
OL,11,Fthe ice in a glacier binds together
OL,12,Fhuge quantities of mud and scree and
OL,13,Frock, so when the ice melts much more
OL,14,Fthan water comes down a mountainside.
