OL,3,C'In 40 seconds, everything was gone':
OL,4,CThe village destroyed by climate change
OL,6,FProfessor Stuart Lane, a British
OL,7,Fglaciologist who lives in these
OL,8,Fmountains, and teaches at the
OL,9,FUniversity of Lausanne, says that as
OL,10,Fgood as Swiss engineering may be, you
OL,11,Fcannot engineer away a problem as big
OL,12,Fas the one that hit Blatten.
