OL,3,C'In 40 seconds, everything was gone':
OL,4,CThe village destroyed by climate change
OL,6,FIndeed, difficult decisions may have
OL,7,Fto be taken about moving whole towns
OL,8,For villages out of the way of
OL,9,Fcollapsing valley walls.
OL,11,F"The only way you can get a glacier
OL,12,Fback is by increasing snow in winter
OL,13,Fand reducing ice melt in summer", he
OL,14,Fsaid. "So only with a reversion to the
OL,15,Fclimate of 50-60 years ago will you
OL,16,Fsee glaciers come back again".
OL,18,FAnd you don't have to be a top
OL,19,Fscientist to know how unlikely that is.
